title: Bring your pet home to Stoneleigh at the Reserve! We accept pets!
posting_body: ['2 Bedroom  2 Bathroom | 1092 sq ft | $1810 - $1865/Month', 'Stoneleigh at the Reserve', '5200 Annapolis Ln N', 'Plymouth, MN 55446', 'show contact info', 'Description:', "The only thing that rivals Stoneleigh's exceptional property is our premium location that's just 15 miles northwest of Minneapolis.", "Here you'll have easy access to I-494, and a public bus stop is just steps outside our front door.", "The Reserve Park is a five-minute walk down the street: it's a great place to have a picnic, go for a walk, or let the kids run and play.", "Just down the road, you'll find Rockford Road Plaza where you can pick up necessities at Target, grab a quick burger at Five Guys, and discover the latest fashions at Kohl's.", 'Apartment Amenities:', '➢ Air Conditioning', '➢ Ceiling Fans', 'In Select Units', '➢ Dining Room', '➢ Dishwasher', '➢ Full-Size Washer/Dryer in Every Home', '➢ Garbage Disposal', '➢ Pantry', 'In Select Units', '➢ Patio/Balcony In Select Units', '➢ Vaulted Ceiling In Select Units', '➢ Walk-In Closets In Select Units', 'Our Residents Enjoy:', '➢ Bike Storage', '➢ Coffee Station', '➢ Conference Room', '➢ Elevator', '➢ Fitness Center', '➢ Free Weights', '➢ Picnic Area', '➢ Pool', '➢ Recycling', '➢ Resident Lounge', '➢ Barbecue/Grill Area', '➢ Business Center', '➢ Cardio Machines', '➢ Complimentary DVD/Video Rental', '➢ Controlled Access Building', '➢ Disposal Chutes', '➢ Planned Social Activities', '➢ Racquetball Court', '➢ Reserveable Clubhouse', '➢ Wake Up With Weidner Continental Breakfast', 'Additional Details:', 'Deposit: Call', 'Terms: Variable', 'Pets: Dogs and Cats Allowed:', 'Fees and deposits apply, please contact the community office for additional information.', '100 lb Weight Limit.', '2 Pet Limit.', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '99EAC36B23684BC']
